            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">歐洲主要股市收市下跌，英法股市自上日紀錄高位回落。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">英國富時100指數報10627點，跌59點，跌幅近0.6%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">法國CAC指數報8398點，跌30點，跌幅近0.4%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">德國DAX指數報25043點，跌234點，跌幅0.9%。</p>\n</div>",
